  "commentary": "With SPX at 6781.17 sitting just above the 6774 GEX flip in a PIN regime, dealers are currently long gamma and will sell into any move toward the massive 6800 gamma wall (54.3B), creating strong resistance as they hedge delta by selling futures. The thick wall of positive gamma from 6780-6800 should act as a ceiling, while the negative gamma pocket at 6765 provides a potential magnet lower where dealers would flip to buying. Watch for rejection at 6800 and potential mean reversion back toward 6774-6780, especially given the wall_break event just detected.\n\nBottom line: expect the market to get pinned between 6774-6800 with upside resistance strongest near 6800.",
